        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks CD for new [2d] edition of <hi rend="italic">Orchids</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Mentions some observations on dimorphic plants.</p> 
<p>Reports on a third species of <hi rend="italic">Pontederia</hi> [see <hi rend="italic">Forms of flowers</hi>, p. 185].</p> 
            <p>Describes some unusual grasses.</p>
            <p>Reports rumours from southern Brazil concerning the existence of a gigantic subterranean animal.</p>
        </abstract>
